<br>
“Nothing,” she said plainly as she removed her arm from Lex’s touch. “There’s nothing you can say or do to make me ever forgive you.” Neither of them saw Bishop walk up next to them.<br>
<br>
“So you really are immune to the Luthor charm,” he mused. Lex shot him a look, but he ignored it. “I’m sorry if I misjudged you Chloe. Allow me to make it up to you,” he said in a sincere voice. She closed her eyes for a moment and swore under her breath.<br>
<br>
