<br>
“It was nice spending time with you again, but I should really be going now. I’m supposed to be shopping,” she said. Lois arched an eyebrow at her. She knew her cousin well enough to know that she was trying to get out of answering Lex’s unspoken question of whether she actually did like him or not, which meant that she probably did. Lois and Lex stood up too.<br>
<br>
